  "heading_path": "机械波 / 多普勒效应",
  "intensity": "STRUCTURAL",
  "line_count": 43,
  "masked_text": "[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02073:8e7148a83e2e]]\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02074:bf70dd081875]]\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02075:c5376617973e]]\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02076:ff2eb9e78880]]{solution}\n分开算两次多普勒，再取频差。对来自 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02077:16048af5f80e]] 的声波，[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02078:16048af5f80e]] 静止而观察者远离 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02079:16048af5f80e]]，故\n [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02080:1828d8d9b738]] \n对来自 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02081:07b947148267]] 的声波，声源和观察者相向运动，故\n [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02082:66ad510c847c]] \n拍频为\n [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02083:fb59dc17d02d]] \n所以观察者听到来自 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02084:16048af5f80e]] 的频率约为 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02085:1e84c8708cb1]]，来自 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02086:07b947148267]] 的频率约为 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02087:77381d1274a3]]，拍频约为 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02088:9b32c3005584]]。\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02089:06b3847e1b6f]]{solution}\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02090:0ec96250ce47]]\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02091:ff2eb9e78880]]{solution}\n火车速度 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02092:1afdc71a400b]]，于是\n [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02093:385cbdedb195]] \n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02094:06b3847e1b6f]]{solution}\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02095:18ed4700cd80]]\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02096:ff2eb9e78880]]{solution}\n速度 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02097:76b434149bea]]。两列车速率相同，故 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02098:63cf117804ed]]，于是\n [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02099:9e9978afb863]] \n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02100:06b3847e1b6f]]{solution}\n",
