  "read_only_context_after": "[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02101:709a26eb5332]]",
  "read_only_context_before": "弦上的波速为 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02066:cec39e01aa76]]。于是基频对应 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02067:2ec462ed7091]]：\n [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02068:b227c7644a38]] \n更高次谐频为\n [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02069:fdac970f1715]] \n基频约为 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02070:b2b88cbbf3da]]，各次谐频满足 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02071:a238a679fafc]]。谐频是基频的整数倍，是因为弦长里必须塞下整数个半波长。\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02072:06b3847e1b6f]]{solution}",
